        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px">
        <h3>Pipeline <span class="badge">Lead ‚Üí Proposal ‚Üí Won</span></h3>
        <div class="grid grid-3" id="pipeline">
          <div class="column">
